Substantive modifications under `ddyolo26/` (AGPL §5(a))
--------------------------------------------------------

The following files contain non-trivial modifications relative to upstream
Ultralytics 8.4.41. Trivial changes (PaConvert-generated symbol renames,
header banners, log message localization) are not enumerated. Use
`grep -rn "Modifications Copyright (C) 2026 Dengdxx" ddyolo26/` for the
full per-file list.

- `ddyolo26/__init__.py` — package re-export surface narrowed to detect/segment.
- `ddyolo26/nn/tasks.py` — `load_checkpoint` rewritten for Paddle state-dict
  loading; `nc` injection fix to recover model class count from checkpoint.
- `ddyolo26/nn/autobackend.py` — Paddle checkpoint loading and ONNX/RKNN
  inference adapted for this fork; `.pt` (PyTorch) load path replaced by
  Paddle loader.
- `ddyolo26/nn/modules/head.py` — `Detect` / `Segment` / `Segment26` extended
  with `export_dual_raw` switch and `_forward_export` paths for RKNN INT8.
- `ddyolo26/nn/modules/conv.py`, `block.py`, `activation.py`, `utils.py` —
  PyTorch ops translated to Paddle equivalents; activation fusion adjusted.
- `ddyolo26/engine/exporter.py` — ONNX/RKNN/TensorRT export paths adapted for
  Paddle weights; unsupported upstream export formats are not documented as
  public deployment routes.
- `ddyolo26/engine/predictor.py`, `validator.py`, `model.py`, `results.py` —
  Paddle device handling and tensor type adaptation.
- `ddyolo26/data/{base,augment,loaders,utils,split,__init__}.py` —
  dataloader / tensor calls translated to Paddle.
- `ddyolo26/utils/downloads.py` — Paddle-only local weight resolution and
  generic dataset/resource download helpers.

Project-specific original files
-------------------------------

- `ddyolo26/paddle_utils.py` — Paddle/PyTorch compatibility shim for
  PaConvert output and Paddle runtime API gaps.
- `ddyolo26/version.py` — PaddleYOLO-RKNN version metadata.
- `ddyolo26/utils/runtime.py` — compatibility re-export for the Paddle runtime
  helper module.

- `train.py` and `tools/eval/` —
  Paddle/ONNX/RKNN unified evaluation harness with RGB calibration fix.
- `tools/fix_paddle_onnx.py` — Paddle ONNX graph compatibility utility.
- `export/`, `quant/`, `scripts/`, `bench/` — RK3588 export, quantization,
  board-side benchmarking and NEON tail microbench.

